Hi Tue,
As described and tested by Kris, setting alsoCheckVia =3D true in t=
he SurtPrefixedDecideRule should generally work in the way you want.

Looki=
ng at the decide rules you pasted though, having the TooManyHopsDecideRule =
"maxHops" value=3D"1" set there would prevent you from getting the pdf in t=
he particular example you gave.

Lauren Ko
